== Making directories for Vagrant

This appendix walks you through making the correct directories in you *host* operating system. This could be windows or MacOS. If you are working in Linux, it makes no sense to use Vagrant. Instead, you should use <<Using the LSDTopoToolsSetup.py script,our script LSDTopoToolsSetup.py>>. 

